{"tid":239971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電騙案受害人「年輕化」　多為大學生","createTime":"2017-05-12T05:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T12:49:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96656eee92bebf11320521b7fe08ad7c2a3dc206","tid":239971,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"近日電騙案受害人大多「年輕」及「學歷高」。據警方數字，今年首季共127宗有損失電騙案中，事主以30歲以下最多，有41宗個案，佔整體3成3；其次是30歲至40歲，有21宗，佔整體1成7，其中有高中和大學以上程度的人士是損失金額最大的一群，高中程度受害人的損失金額約2000萬元，有大學以上學歷受害人的損失數字為1300萬元。「假冒官員」是電騙案騙徒最「賺錢」的手法，首季共騙走3700萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n本月10日晚上9時許，警方接獲一名姓李（20歲）港大內地女生報案，指自己遇上「電騙黨」，先後8次將約值27000港元的人民幣轉帳給騙徒。 <br />\n<br />\n上月20日，一名姓李（29歲）中大工程學系內地博士生亦報案，收到冒充入境處電話，指他干犯刑事罪行要求他發入一個虛構網站輸入內地銀行戶口資料，男生被套料後失去74萬人民幣。 <br />\n<br />\n一名姓鄧（23歲）中大博士生上月亦遇到假冒內地海關的騙徒來電，向父母及朋友借取300萬人民幣，將總數390萬人民幣匯至自己的內地銀行帳戶，結果被騙徒全數提走。 <br />\n<br />\n今年3月5日下午4時許，一名姓蘇（32歲）科大學生報案，指日前接獲冒稱入境處及內地公安的來電，指他涉及洗黑錢案，着他用手機下載流動應用程式，填寫個人及銀行戶口資料，及後發現被人由銀行匯走26萬元人民幣。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170512/mobile/bkn-20170512103656963-0512_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170512%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170512103656963-0512_00822_001.html&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUinIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=0177a265\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170512/mobile/bkn-20170512103656963-0512_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f87aa6a53dbf32c868f59c65e30c0250ba70173","tid":239971,"uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"X: 年輕化 <br />\nV: 中国化"},{"pid":"0a7aaea8e7f5220db053165c6c0f06f9088ef511","tid":239971,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"4個入面2個都內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a835cf9500cd3a702a67621bf3a288c26973e88","tid":239971,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4個入面2個都內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係4個都係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0a4390c3c35d56c459a0225ad0669a041cb831","tid":239971,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7803b119375017cd588e1823e69f60e4931ad4c","tid":239971,"uid":3007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"有錢黎香港爭學位<br />\n但因為D錢都係貪污返黎既<br />\n咪咁撚死蠢中伏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2726fe19081f82c6b6e429c77232b33160876c","tid":239971,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"普通大學生點會有大陸銀行戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64ba63febf3c62254efa4f0e8f7011ea44f4910","tid":239971,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"大陸又屈尻年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   好尾機"},{"pid":"a4ece81e33396ff2735a0d8d3fadce3779575c7e","tid":239971,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢黎香港爭學位<br />\n但因為D錢都係貪污返黎既<br />\n咪咁撚死蠢中伏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdcd7d366ee27827976f952a8c7332d755cc098","tid":239971,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"中國人黎香港讀大學=大學生<br />\nset and subset既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341583896daa4e11398ac12fc328847cf12d07b1","tid":239971,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4個入面2個都內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj